      <title>Planning some changes</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/arh_jdebug/forum/general/planning_some_changes</link>
      <description>As new member in the project, I's like to discuss some ideas before committing them:&#13;
&#13;
1. use pure-js based loading. This beacuse you can not guarantee that the debug_toolbar.tpl is loaded at all times (I generally have it disabled)&#13;
&#13;
2. use design.ini to enable/disable the extension instead of providing a custom param in debugjquery.ini&#13;
&#13;
3. rename images so that they use lowercase, english filenames&#13;
&#13;
4. rename the module name and ini file name so that they're consistent with the extension&#13;
&#13;
5. if possible, do away completely with the custom fetch functions&#13;
&#13;
Comments?</description>
